---
// Hero page section extraída de index.astro
---

<section id="inicio" class="hero-main hero-yellow">
  <div class="hero-content-main">
    <h1 class="hero-title-main">Ana Ruiz</h1>
    <h2 class="hero-title-main hero-title-secondary">Especialista en Growth Marketing</h2>
    <div class="hero-subtitles-group">
      <p class="hero-subtitle-main">Estoy aquí para darle sentido común a tu estrategia y moverla contigo
        <span class="hero-subtitle-secondary">
          <span style="color: var(--color-info)">Estrategia</span> · 
          <span style="color: var(--color-info)">IA</span> · 
          <span style="color: var(--color-info)">Procesos</span> · 
          <span style="color: var(--color-info)">Crecimiento</span> · 
          <span style="color: var(--color-info)">Sentido común</span>
        </span>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<style>
  .hero-main {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    justify-content: flex-start;
  background: url('/images/anahero.jpg') right center/cover no-repeat;
    padding: 3em 2em;
    margin-bottom: 0;
    min-height: 350px;
    gap: 2em;
    box-sizing: border-box;
    border-radius: 0;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 3;
    height: 700px;
    text-align: left;
  background-size: cover;
  background-position: right center;
  transition: background-position 0.3s, background-size 0.3s;
  }
  @media (max-width: 1200px) {
    .hero-main {
      background-size: cover;
      background-position: right center;
    }
  }
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .hero-main {
      background-size: cover;
      background-position: right center;
      flex-direction: column;
      text-align: left;
      padding: 2em 1em;
    }
    .hero-img-main {
      margin-top: 2em;
    }
  }
  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .hero-main {
      background-size: cover;
      background-position: right center;
      height: auto !important;
      min-height: unset !important;
      background-color: var(--color-secondary, #fce331) !important;
    }
  }
  .hero-yellow {
    border-radius: 0 !important;
    box-shadow: none !important;
  }
  .hero-content-main {
    flex: 1 1 60%;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: flex-start;
    align-items: flex-start;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    text-align: left;
  }
  .hero-title-main {
    font-family: 'Poppins', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
    font-size: 3.6em;
    font-weight: 800;
    margin: 0 0 0.1em 0;
    line-height: 1.02;
    color: #222;
    letter-spacing: -1px;
    text-align: left;
  }
  .hero-title-secondary {
    font-size: 2.2em;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin: 0 0 0.5em 0;
    color: #222;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    text-align: left;
  }
  .hero-subtitles-group {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: flex-start;
    justify-content: flex-end;
    margin-top: 1.2em;
    margin-bottom: 0;
    min-height: 90px;
    text-align: left;
  }
  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .hero-subtitles-group {
      margin-bottom: 10px !important;
    }
  }
  .hero-subtitle-main {
    font-size: 1.25em;
    color: #444;
    margin: 0;
    font-weight: 400;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 0.2em;
    text-align: left;
  }
  .hero-subtitle-secondary {
    font-size: 1.25em;
    color: #b0b0b0;
    margin: 0;
    font-weight: 400;
    display: block;
    text-align: left;
  }
  .hero-img-main {
    flex: 1 1 40%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    z-index: 10;
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .hero-img-main img {
    width: 220px;
    height: 220px;
    object-fit: cover;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: #fff;
    border: 6px solid #fff;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
    display: block;
    margin: 0 auto;
    z-index: 11;
    position: relative;
    pointer-events: auto;
  }
</style>
